    <item>
      <title>жЂјтј╗ТЌЦС╗ўсЂДGithubсЂ«УЇЅсѓњућЪсѓёсЂЎ</title>
      <link>/blog-github-contributions-before-date.html</link>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 Jan 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      <guid>/blog-github-contributions-before-date.html</guid>
      <description>&lt;h4 id=&#34;сЂ»сЂўсѓЂсЂФ&#34;&gt;сЂ»сЂўсѓЂсЂФ&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;сЂЊсЂ«сЃќсЃГсѓ░сЂ»Github PagesсЂДжЂІућесЂЌсЂдсЂёсЂдсђЂС╗іт╣┤сЂ«уЏ«ТеЎсЂїсђјсЃќсЃГсѓ░сѓњт«џТюЪуџёсЂФТЏ┤Тќ░сЂЌсЂдсѓбсѓдсЃѕсЃЌсЃЃсЃѕсЂЎсѓІсђЈсЂЊсЂесЂфсЂ«сЂДтЈ»УдќтїќсЂЌсЂЪсЂёсЂеУђЃсЂѕсЂдсЂёсЂЪсђѓGithubсЂФсЂ»Contribution сѓњтЈ»УдќтїќсЂЎсѓІжђџуД░сђјУЇЅсђЈсЂїсЂѓсѓІсЂ«сЂДсЂЊсѓїсѓњСй┐сЂБсЂдтЈ»УдќтїќсЂЌсѓѕсЂєсЂеУђЃсЂѕсЂЪсђѓ&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;img src=&#34;image-20200109180941763.png&#34; alt=&#34;image-20200109180941763&#34; style=&#34;zoom: 50%;&#34; /&gt;
&lt;p&gt;СИђТќ╣сђЂGithub PagesсѓњСй┐сЂётДІсѓЂсѓІтЅЇсЂФТЏ┤Тќ░сЂЌсЂЪУеўС║ІсѓѓтцџсЂёсЂ«сЂДТЏ┤Тќ░сЂЌсЂЪТЌЦсѓњContributionсЂФтЈЇТўасЂЋсЂЏсЂЪсЂёсЂеТђЮсЂёсђЂжЂјтј╗ТЌЦС╗ўсЂДGithubсЂ«УЇЅсѓњућЪсѓёсЂЎТќ╣Т│ЋсѓњУф┐сЂ╣сЂдсЂ┐сЂЪсђѓ&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h4 id=&#34;Тќ╣Т│Ћ&#34;&gt;Тќ╣Т│Ћ&lt;/h4&gt;
&lt;p&gt;УЇЅсЂїућЪсЂѕсѓІТЮАС╗ХсЂ»СИІУеўсЂ«жђџсѓісђѓcommitсѓёissueсђЂpull requestсЂїТЮАС╗ХсЂесЂфсѓІсђѓуЅ╣сЂФсѓйсЃ╝сѓ╣сѓ│сЃ╝сЃЅсЂ«С┐«ТГБсЂ»СИЇУдЂсЂДсЂЊсѓїсЂасЂЉсЂД&lt;del&gt;тЂйжђа&lt;/del&gt;ContributionтЄ║ТЮЦсѓІсђѓ&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://help.github.com/en/github/setting-up-and-managing-your-github-profile/viewing-contributions-on-your-profile&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;https://help.github.com/en/github/setting-up-and-managing-your-github-profile/viewing-contributions-on-your-profile&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;what-counts-as-a-contributionhttpshelpgithubcomengithubsetting-up-and-managing-your-github-profileviewing-contributions-on-your-profilewhat-counts-as-a-contribution&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;https://help.github.com/en/github/setting-up-and-managing-your-github-profile/viewing-contributions-on-your-profile#what-counts-as-a-contribution&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;What counts as a contribution&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;p&gt;On your profile page, certain actions count as contributions:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Committing to a repository&amp;rsquo;s default branch or &lt;code&gt;gh-pages&lt;/code&gt; branch&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Opening an issue&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proposing a pull request&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Submitting a pull request review&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;С╗ітЏъсЂ»AuthorDateсѓњжЂјтј╗ТЌЦС╗ўсЂФсЂфсѓІсѓѕсЂєсЂФ&lt;code&gt;git commit&lt;/code&gt;сѓ│сЃъсЃ│сЃЅсЂФ&lt;code&gt;--date&lt;/code&gt;сѓњТїЄт«џсЂЎсѓІсЂЊсЂесЂФсЂЌсЂЪсђѓсЂЮсЂ«тЙїсЂ»pushсЂЌсЂдухѓсѓЈсѓісђѓ&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h5 id=&#34;сѓ│сЃъсЃ│сЃЅ&#34;&gt;сѓ│сЃъсЃ│сЃЅ&lt;/h5&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-sh&#34; data-lang=&#34;sh&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;git commit --allow-empty -m &lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;COMMIT&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt; --date&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;s2&#34;&gt;&amp;#34;Dec 29 23:59:59 2019 +0900&amp;#34;&lt;/span&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;git push origin master
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h5 id=&#34;уб║УфЇ&#34;&gt;уб║УфЇ&lt;/h5&gt;
&lt;div class=&#34;highlight&#34;&gt;&lt;pre tabindex=&#34;0&#34; class=&#34;chroma&#34;&gt;&lt;code class=&#34;language-sh&#34; data-lang=&#34;sh&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;git log --pretty&lt;span class=&#34;o&#34;&gt;=&lt;/span&gt;fuller
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;commit d0d02bd117419f4aacc7d8f16e78f192ec8ce79d
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;Author:     Imazato &amp;lt;xxxxx.xxxxxx@gmail.com&amp;gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;AuthorDate: Sun Dec &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;29&lt;/span&gt; 23:59:59 &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;2019&lt;/span&gt; +0900
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;Commit:     Imazato &amp;lt;xxxxx.xxxxxx@gmail.com&amp;gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;CommitDate: Wed Jan &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;8&lt;/span&gt; 17:46:25 &lt;span class=&#34;m&#34;&gt;2020&lt;/span&gt; +0900
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;cl&#34;&gt;    COMMIT
&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h5 id=&#34;ухљТъю&#34;&gt;ухљТъю&lt;/h5&gt;
&lt;p&gt;УеўС║ІсЂІсѓЅТЏ┤Тќ░ТЌЦС╗ўсѓњт╝ЋсЂБт╝хсЂБсЂдсЂЇсЂдсђЂсѓ│сЃъсЃ│сЃЅсѓњт«ЪУАїсЂЎсѓІсЂЊсЂесЂДжЂјтј╗ТЌЦС╗ўсЂДсѓѓУЇЅсЂїућЪсЂѕсЂЪсђѓУЇЅсЂїућЪсЂѕсЂдсЂёсЂфсЂёсЂеУљйсЂАуЮђсЂІсЂфсЂёСйЊсѓњуЏ«ТїЄсЂЎсђѓ&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;















